{"tid":8044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報： 勿盲目跟風換外幣","createTime":"2016-11-28T06:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T00:51:49.000Z","uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f716a8adb62f1ffb06fea5c7122d78cac7a1e543","tid":8044,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"【官媒出口術】《人民日報》： 勿盲目跟風換外幣<br />\n<br />\n2016-11-28 08:19:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2L503.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2L503.jpg&h=be167b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人民幣對美元匯價接連下調，《人民日報》為穩定內地民心，今日刊文談及是否需要換外幣，建議「不宜盲目跟風」。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述專家分析，近來人民幣匯率下行主要是因為美元太強，同期人民幣對一籃子貨幣基本穩定，也不存在長期貶值基礎。個人換外匯要根據自身需求，不宜盲目跟風兌換。如果短期內無剛需，沒有必要提前換匯。相比人民幣，美元存款利率及理財產品收益率並無太大優勢。<br />\n<br />\n中金所研究院首席經濟學家趙慶明認為，如果下月加息落實，美元上漲會暫告一段落，加上近期美聯儲加息影響已逐漸被市場消化，未來包括人民幣在內的非美元貨幣走勢會相對穩定。他說：「對於高淨值、金融資產較多的人群，可以考慮配置一定外幣資產，這類人群往往使用外幣的機會和渠道較多，外幣資產的合理組合有助於減少財富縮水；相反，對於普通家庭，總的金融資產並不多，使用外幣機會也很少，不建議盲目跟風增持美元。」<br />\n<br />\n民生銀行首席研究員溫彬則指，個人考慮配置貨幣籃子，主要還應以自身需求為依據，保證外匯使用和需求的一致性。譬如，目前英鎊價格較低，個人短期內若有去英國旅遊或留學的需求，可以提前持有英鎊，減少匯兌風險和匯率損失。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》<br />\n<br />\nSauce: <br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161128&amp;guid=55974850&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161128%26guid%3D55974850%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=hzNM7YY%2BVeW%2BoBM08pddX8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=b337568b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161128%26guid%3D55974850%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=99d23844\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161128&amp;guid=55974850&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">支爆近了，各位應當睇路</span>"},{"pid":"34c8f1e4c5dc7b66819181f5faa27bb6947d6f89","tid":8044,"uid":20708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"留名待笑"},{"pid":"5b7926b539e818de084e39e107c7b8a12fa56e42","tid":8044,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"人民幣準備變軍票"},{"pid":"85d4ff9a920722c069e092ed09a98666591c2241","tid":8044,"uid":5574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"越叫你唔好換, 就越應該換"},{"pid":"eac987af1e1ed1ecd3c4c9ffc996349b5a979bf5","tid":8044,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"支爆巴打召喚"},{"pid":"31c6fe7a7b00cff3df184c447fe2d7dac5e3df24","tid":8044,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"幾時換美金都係有著數過支那冥幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d15e556d0f8a25acbc0a5d48835d7469db78d3","tid":8044,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"淆到咁"},{"pid":"10ccad3a292183fa87263ff123b0853baca77bf3","tid":8044,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"將五年前五姨婆果100蚊人仔既利是唱返做港紙，為國家一份力先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d520269ae166701214d3cebc2bc3afbe37052a","tid":8044,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越叫你唔好換, 就越應該換</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且要狠狠咁換 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b83f49628a2fb99a090844cd2c39b25f3de03a3","tid":8044,"uid":22285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"好彩早半年清曬啲人民幣定期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd72e0fb9fb7fefa89112ad69152e06ae05728c","tid":8044,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":